= Installation =

<pre>
$ dnf install etcd
</pre>

= Configuration =

The configuration is located at /etc/etcd/etcd.conf.

= Systemd =

The systemd unit file is located at /usr/lib/systemd/system/etcd.service.

To start the service:

<pre>
$ systemctl start etcd
</pre>

To stop the service:

<pre>
$ systemctl stop etcd
</pre>

